Make web front end in ClojureScript.
Use liberator to make a rest api the clojurescript front end can
   interact with.
Store documents in a datomic db.
When first starting the app, ask for a save file to load existing state.
Split database logic out of web logic.


DB Schema:

Document
-Name   :db.type/string
-Text   :db.type/string
-Source :db.type/string
-Image? - not for now

;; Edges can be calculated from the documents.

Edge
;; Note that the edge is undirected, so Doc1 and Doc2 are interchangeable.
-Doc1     :db.type/ref
-Doc2     :db.type/ref
-Distance :db.type/double
-Source   :db.type/keyword (either :user or :system)